        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "As a mortal you always knew you were the kinfolk of the tribe of werewolves known as the Shadow Lords. You helped form The Spiral Sign of Sabbat who were Lupine Kinfolk, based on the prophecy of Xerxes that a Lupine Kinfolk will ascend the throne of Caine and as Regent of the Sabbat will lead the sect to victory against the Antediluveans.  You and your pack are constantly searching for the right Lupine Kinfolk and once they are on the verge of changing into werewolves you embrace them in hopes of turning them into the Avatar of Caine.  Most simply become vampires, others die in great agony.  You have used your knowledge of the Lupines, or Garou, to develop allies amongst the Black Spiral Dancers - the kin of your pack leader Feast.  While you long ago stopped believing that your pack will successfully create an Avatar of Caine you know the rest of the Pack hasn't come to that conclusion. You hope to develop strong allies with othe LA Sabbat and eventually lead the pack in a new direction.  This war is a perfect chance to prove your power and the power of your allies."
        ],
